    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to PyAtSpi2</title>

      <para>
        The <application>PyAtSpi2</application> package contains
        <application>Python</application> bindings for the core
        components of the <application>GNOME</application>
        Accessibility.
      </para>

      &lfs130_checked;

