      </para>

    </sect3>

    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of PyAtSpi2</title>

      <para>
        To build <application>PyAtSpi2</application>, run the following
        commands:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

meson setup --prefix=/usr --buildtype=release -D enable_tests=true .. &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>


      <para>
        To run the tests issue: <command>ninja test</command>. The tests need
        to be run in a graphical environment.
      </para>

      <para>
        To install the module, run the following command as the &root; user:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install</userinput></screen>

    </sect3>

